<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sat, 01 Jun 2024 02:27:37 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>哈马斯：准备“积极”应对以色列提议，其中包括加沙永久停火</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-01/ty-article-live/hamas-ready-to-deal-positively-with-proposal-that-includes-a-permanent-gaza-cease-fire/0000018f-d178-d673-ab8f-f7f89e9b0000</link><description>拜登提出了以色列与哈马斯达成人质、停火协议的三阶段提议 ■ 内塔尼亚胡表示向哈马斯提出的新提议符合以色列的目标 ■ 布林肯与土耳其、约旦和沙特阿拉伯讨论加沙计划 ■ 哈马斯发布人质诺亚的录音加沙囚禁的阿加马尼 ■ 美国人质家属赞扬拜登敦促哈马斯接受停火建议</description><pubDate>Sat, 01 Jun 2024 01:55:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-01/ty-article-live/hamas-ready-to-deal-positively-with-proposal-that-includes-a-permanent-gaza-cease-fire/0000018f-d178-d673-ab8f-f7f89e9b0000</guid></item><item><title>为什么以色列不能错过另一个与沙特阿拉伯关系正常化的机会</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-06-01/ty-article-opinion/.premium/why-israel-cant-miss-yet-another-opportunity-to-normalize-ties-with-saudi-arabia/0000018f-cfdb-dd44-a3ef-cfdbc2c90000</link><description>这并不是以色列第一次放弃与沙特建立关系的机会。但这一次，说“不”就意味着拒绝冲出我们的贫民窟并作为合作伙伴和盟友进入该地区的机会</description><pubDate>Fri, 31 May 2024 21:11:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-06-01/ty-article-opinion/.premium/why-israel-cant-miss-yet-another-opportunity-to-normalize-ties-with-saudi-arabia/0000018f-cfdb-dd44-a3ef-cfdbc2c90000</guid></item><item><title>美国国会领导人正式邀请内塔尼亚胡在国会联席会议上发表讲话</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-05-31/ty-article/.premium/u-s-congressional-leaders-invite-netanyahu-to-address-joint-session-of-congress/0000018f-d021-dbdb-a59f-d1690b560000</link><description>包括查克·舒默在内的国会领导人正式邀请内塔尼亚胡在国会发表讲话，该讲话已经引起民主党议员的强烈反对，其中许多人发誓要抵制以色列在加沙战争中的行为</description><pubDate>Fri, 31 May 2024 20:27:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-05-31/ty-article/.premium/u-s-congressional-leaders-invite-netanyahu-to-address-joint-session-of-congress/0000018f-d021-dbdb-a59f-d1690b560000</guid></item><item><title>在希伯伦，巴勒斯坦人现在渴望实行 10 月 7 日之前存在的种族隔离制度</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2024-05-31/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/in-hebron-palestinians-now-long-for-apartheid-as-it-existed-before-october-7/0000018f-cfe6-d5bc-a1bf-dff672570000</link><description>自 10 月 7 日以来，希伯伦巴勒斯坦人的生活就不一样了。经过两个月几乎完全封锁后，他们现在每天晚上 7 点到早上 7 点都被限制在家里。以色列士兵和定居者的错误逮捕、暴力和羞辱是他们每天的遭遇</description><pubDate>Fri, 31 May 2024 19:56:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2024-05-31/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/in-hebron-palestinians-now-long-for-apartheid-as-it-existed-before-october-7/0000018f-cfe6-d5bc-a1bf-dff672570000</guid></item><item><title>拜登敦促哈马斯接受以色列全面的新停火提议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2024-05-31/ty-article/.premium/biden-urges-hamas-to-accept-comprehensive-new-israeli-cease-fire-proposal/0000018f-cfcd-d5bc-a1bf-dffd47550000</link><description>根据拜登提出的以色列三阶段提案，总统敦促以色列拒绝内部压力，不要错过支持“不明的全面胜利概念”的时机</description><pubDate>Fri, 31 May 2024 18:24:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2024-05-31/ty-article/.premium/biden-urges-hamas-to-accept-comprehensive-new-israeli-cease-fire-proposal/0000018f-cfcd-d5bc-a1bf-dffd47550000</guid></item><item><title>甘茨在政府任职逾期，现在内塔尼亚胡已经不在乎他笨拙的操纵</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-31/ty-article/.premium/gantz-overstayed-in-the-govt-now-netanyahu-doesnt-care-about-his-clumsy-maneuvering/0000018f-ce78-dc8d-a18f-fffdda840000</link><description>诚然，随着加沙战事的持续，甘茨在战时内阁中的地位日趋软弱，而且他威胁要在 6 月 8 日之前辞职的威胁看起来是经过深思熟虑的。但内塔尼亚胡可能严重低估了以色列人对其总理的不满</description><pubDate>Fri, 31 May 2024 17:27:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-31/ty-article/.premium/gantz-overstayed-in-the-govt-now-netanyahu-doesnt-care-about-his-clumsy-maneuvering/0000018f-ce78-dc8d-a18f-fffdda840000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军将军巴拉克·希拉姆 (Barak Hiram) 是谁？他下令用坦克向基布兹一处房屋开火，里面有 13 名人质？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-31/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/who-is-the-idf-general-who-ordered-tank-fire-on-a-kibbutz-home-with-13-hostages-inside/0000018f-ca16-da41-a9cf-db3eaa080000</link><description>双桅船。巴拉克·希拉姆将军在 10 月 7 日的战斗中发出了最具争议的命令：向哈马斯恐怖分子扣押人质的贝埃里基布兹房屋发射坦克炮弹。与认识这位勇敢、鹰派军官的人交谈后，我们发现他是一个打破成见的人。这是以色列国防军的新面孔吗？</description><pubDate>Fri, 31 May 2024 16:23:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-31/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/who-is-the-idf-general-who-ordered-tank-fire-on-a-kibbutz-home-with-13-hostages-inside/0000018f-ca16-da41-a9cf-db3eaa080000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第 238 天：法国因拉法行动禁止以色列公司参加军火博览会</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-05-31/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-238-france-bans-israeli-companies-from-arms-expo-over-rafah-op/0000018f-cf70-d673-ab8f-fff8e7550000</link><description>哈马斯公布以色列人质诺亚·阿加马尼的录音 ■ 人质家庭论坛：内塔尼亚胡政府“做出了牺牲人质的有意识和深思熟虑的决定” ■ 由于以色列的行为，法国禁止以色列公司参加下个月举行的年度欧洲武器和国防工业展览会拉法 ■ 美国、英国军队称他们袭击了也门的胡塞武装目标 ■ 战争进入 238 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Fri, 31 May 2024 16:23:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-05-31/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-238-france-bans-israeli-companies-from-arms-expo-over-rafah-op/0000018f-cf70-d673-ab8f-fff8e7550000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯公布以色列人质诺亚·阿加马尼的录音</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-31/ty-article/hamas-releases-voice-recording-of-hostage-noa-argamani/0000018f-cf59-da41-a9cf-df7f836c0000</link><description>来自贝尔谢巴的 26 岁阿伽玛尼 (Argamani) 与她的伴侣阿维纳坦·奥尔 (Avinatan Or) 一起在 Nova 音乐节上被绑架。战争初期有人看到她骑摩托车被绑架到加沙</description><pubDate>Fri, 31 May 2024 16:06:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-31/ty-article/hamas-releases-voice-recording-of-hostage-noa-argamani/0000018f-cf59-da41-a9cf-df7f836c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列妇女因在社交媒体上批评战争的帖子而被拘留并蒙住眼睛</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-31/ty-article/.premium/israeli-woman-detained-blindfolded-over-social-media-posts-criticizing-war/0000018f-cee4-da41-a9cf-dffe8ad90000</link><description>警方称，以色列阿拉伯妇女拉莎·卡里姆·哈拉米因在社交媒体上发布“反以色列国防军士兵和反以色列”帖子而被捕。国家检察官办公室表示，警方在逮捕过程中的身体行为原因“尚不清楚”</description><pubDate>Fri, 31 May 2024 15:09:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-31/ty-article/.premium/israeli-woman-detained-blindfolded-over-social-media-posts-criticizing-war/0000018f-cee4-da41-a9cf-dffe8ad90000</guid></item><item><title>比利时根特大学与所有以色列大学断绝联系</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2024-05-31/ty-article/belgiums-ghent-university-severs-ties-with-all-israeli-universities/0000018f-ce8b-d117-a7ef-ffffeaa00000</link><description>根特的亲巴勒斯坦抗议者一直抗议以色列对加沙的军事进攻，并自五月初以来一直占领该校部分校园。该大学已与 3 个以色列机构断绝关系，但与 18 个以色列学术机构保持着持续的合作关系</description><pubDate>Fri, 31 May 2024 12:11:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2024-05-31/ty-article/belgiums-ghent-university-severs-ties-with-all-israeli-universities/0000018f-ce8b-d117-a7ef-ffffeaa00000</guid></item><item><title>明尼苏达大学学术期刊为抵制以色列学者道歉</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-05-31/ty-article/.premium/university-of-minnesota-academic-journal-apologizes-for-boycotting-israeli-scholar/0000018f-ce5e-dc8d-a18f-ffdfcf520000</link><description>《文化评论》的编辑写信给一位提交论文供审阅的以色列学者，“我们遗憾地通知您，由于该期刊遵守 BDS 指南，我们无法考虑您提交的论文发表”</description><pubDate>Fri, 31 May 2024 11:28:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-05-31/ty-article/.premium/university-of-minnesota-academic-journal-apologizes-for-boycotting-israeli-scholar/0000018f-ce5e-dc8d-a18f-ffdfcf520000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军公布了两名在加沙战斗中丧生的以色列士兵的名字</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-31/ty-article/idf-names-two-israeli-soldiers-killed-in-gaza-combat/0000018f-ce02-d117-a7ef-ff7f99a40000</link><description>来自凯撒利亚的 24 岁中士（预备）阿达尔·加夫里尔 (Adar Gavriel) 在加沙北部的战斗中阵亡。来自耶路撒冷的 20 岁耶霍纳坦·埃利亚斯中士在加沙南部的战斗中阵亡。以色列国防军表示，在同一事件中，另一名士兵受重伤。</description><pubDate>Fri, 31 May 2024 09:47:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-31/ty-article/idf-names-two-israeli-soldiers-killed-in-gaza-combat/0000018f-ce02-d117-a7ef-ff7f99a40000</guid></item><item><title>以色列反政府抗议者期待“决定性的”六月，将目光投向耶路撒冷</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-31/ty-article/.premium/israels-anti-government-protesters-look-to-fateful-june-set-sights-on-jerusalem/0000018f-cd76-dc8d-a18f-fdf7fa1f0000</link><description>抗议团体将升级与政府的斗争，并将焦点转向首都，以期在加沙战争一周年之前举行选举并解散议会</description><pubDate>Fri, 31 May 2024 09:31:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-31/ty-article/.premium/israels-anti-government-protesters-look-to-fateful-june-set-sights-on-jerusalem/0000018f-cd76-dc8d-a18f-fdf7fa1f0000</guid></item><item><title>影片讲述了 10 月 7 日付出惨重代价的以色列泰国工人群体的心声</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-31/ty-article-magazine/.premium/film-gives-voice-to-israels-thai-workers-community-that-suffered-badly-on-october-7/0000018f-ca76-d801-a3ef-fb7651ad0000</link><description>纪录片《泰国土地》让我们一睹死海附近的一个农业社区的风采，那里一群紧密团结的泰国工人基本上实现了犹太复国主义的梦想，而他们的以色列雇主却放弃了这个梦想</description><pubDate>Fri, 31 May 2024 07:28:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-31/ty-article-magazine/.premium/film-gives-voice-to-israels-thai-workers-community-that-suffered-badly-on-october-7/0000018f-ca76-d801-a3ef-fb7651ad0000</guid></item><item><title>甘茨退出内塔尼亚胡战时政府对以色列来说是个好消息</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-31/ty-article/.premium/gantzs-exit-from-netanyahus-wartime-government-will-be-good-news-for-israel/0000018f-cb06-dcdc-ad9f-db1683cc0000</link><description>联盟不会被削弱，但抗议活动将会加剧，任何剩余的外交合法性都将消失 ■ 内塔尼亚胡的毒药机器与理智的以色列作战 ■ 新的选举可能会引发地狱般的僵局 ■ 工党终于有了新的领导人</description><pubDate>Fri, 31 May 2024 03:01:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-31/ty-article/.premium/gantzs-exit-from-netanyahus-wartime-government-will-be-good-news-for-israel/0000018f-cb06-dcdc-ad9f-db1683cc0000</guid></item><item><title>即使以色列在拉法的致命行动结束，问题仍然存在：接下来怎么办？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-31/ty-article/.premium/even-when-israels-deadly-rafah-op-is-over-well-still-be-asking-what-next/0000018f-cb05-d801-a3ef-fb0503bd0000</link><description>拉法赫和贾巴利亚正在进行的军事行动已将加沙的以色列人质赶出公众视线 ■ 如果对 10 月 7 日的失败进行真正的调查有任何希望，那可能只是来自平民</description><pubDate>Fri, 31 May 2024 03:00:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-31/ty-article/.premium/even-when-israels-deadly-rafah-op-is-over-well-still-be-asking-what-next/0000018f-cb05-d801-a3ef-fb0503bd0000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯：准备“积极”应对以色列提议，其中包括加沙永久停火</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-31/ty-article-live/hamas-ready-for-complete-agreement-on-hostages-if-israel-stops-war-in-gaza/0000018f-cc5a-d801-a3ef-fd5acac50000</link><description>拜登提出了以色列与哈马斯达成人质、停火协议的三阶段提议 ■ 内塔尼亚胡表示，向哈马斯提出的新提议符合以色列的目标 ■ 以色列军队确认其部队已进入拉法中部 ■ 哈马斯公布了人质诺亚·阿加马尼 (Noa Argamani) 的录音加沙被囚禁 ■以色列国防军称，黎巴嫩最近向以色列北部发射了十五枚火箭弹</description><pubDate>Fri, 31 May 2024 02:00:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-31/ty-article-live/hamas-ready-for-complete-agreement-on-hostages-if-israel-stops-war-in-gaza/0000018f-cc5a-d801-a3ef-fd5acac50000</guid></item><item><title>如何在不威胁他们生活方式的情况下征募极端正统派进入以色列军队</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-05-31/ty-article-opinion/.highlight/how-to-draft-haredim-into-israels-army-without-threatening-their-way-of-life/0000018f-cb90-d323-a98f-dbd97dae0000</link><description>当一个虔诚的极端正统公众与另一个虔诚的国家安全公众对抗时，我们该怎么办？</description><pubDate>Thu, 30 May 2024 23:04:50 GMT</pubDate><